"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?38/31/39411/abstract/13\">",
"      Kapadia SR, Goel SS, Svensson L, et al. Characterization and outcome of patients with severe symptomatic aortic stenosis referred for percutaneous aortic valve replacement. J Thorac Cardiovasc Surg 2009; 137:1430.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
